535
00:38:05,920 --> 00:38:07,500
You poor thing.

536
00:38:07,500 --> 00:38:10,670
Who stabbed you in the back first?

537
00:38:10,670 --> 00:38:14,000
You saw him trying to split up the Chanyeong High class.

538
00:38:15,420 --> 00:38:17,310
At the time that was really...

539
00:38:18,590 --> 00:38:20,380
disappointing.

540
00:38:27,150 --> 00:38:29,690
I think I need time to think about it.

541
00:38:29,690 --> 00:38:31,540
Of course.

542
00:38:32,490 --> 00:38:35,140
Did you decide whom you'd take with you, by chance?

543
00:38:36,040 --> 00:38:42,620
