545
00:38:45,700 --> 00:38:47,480
If you want.

546
00:38:48,260 --> 00:38:51,490
There's something I want to test beforehand.

547
00:38:51,490 --> 00:38:54,790
I know there's a class he wants to teach.

548
00:38:54,790 --> 00:38:57,310
